Down and Dirty Tailoring ~ by Cormath Loremaster<br>
------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
No easy way around it, you have to farm or buy pelts <br>
and silks to work this trade skill. Any size Tailoring Kit <br>
will work as long as all ingredients fit. I use Mask <br>
patterns since they require the least amount of ingredients.<br>
<br>
Silk Swatch (Trivial at 17)<br>
2 Spider Silks<br>
<br>
Patchwork (Trivial at 26) - Use Ruined Pelts<br>
Wolf small /Cat medium /Bear large sizes <br>
Ruined Pelt, Mask Pattern<br>
<br>
Raw Silk (Trivial at 39) - Caster/Monk<br>
Silk Swatch, Mask Pattern <br>
<br>
Studded (Trivial at 57) - Use Medium Quality Pelts<br>
Wolf small /Cat medium /Bear large sizes<br>
MQ Pelt, Metal Stud, Mask Pattern<br>
<br>
Cured Silk (Trivial at 82) - Monk Only<br>
Silk Swatch, Heady Kiola, Mask Pattern<br>
<br>
Handmade Backpack (Trivial at 87)<br>
Backpack Pattern, HQ Bear Skin<br>
(10-slot container, weight 3)<br>
<br>
Reinforced (Trivial at 108) - Use HQ Pelts/Skin <br>
Wolf small /Cat medium /Bear large sizes<br>
HQ Pelt, Steel Boning, Mask Pattern<br>
<br>
Quiver (Trivial at 115)<br>
Quiver Pattern, HQ Cat Pelt<br>
<br>
Wu's Fighting Armor (monk-only, (##) is trivial for that item) <br>
Vial of Viscous Mana, appropriate pattern, <br>
4 Heady Kiolas, appropriate number of Silk Swatches:<br>
Gorget(128), Mask(135), Cap(142), Bracer(135), Mantle(135) - 1 Swatch <br>
Belt(128), Boots(142), Sleeves(151) - 2 Swatches <br>
Cloak(135), Pants(155), Tunic(158) - 3 Swatches<br>
<br>
(As an alternate route if you cannot get Viscous Mana)<br>
Cystalline Silk (all/all) - don't forget the pattern!<br>
Kyla Frostbeard, Cobi Frostbeard at<br>
(Frostbeards Furs and Leathers) sells Silver Thread<br>
Mantle(118) - Silver Thread, 1 Swatch<br>
Gloves(124) - Silver Thread, 2 Swatches<br>
Tunic(131) - Silver Thread, 3 Swatches<br>
<br>
****************************************************<br>
All Velious recipes other than the crystalline silk require the use of <br>
the Coldain Tanners Kit instead of a large sewing kit. (The crystalline<br>
silk can use either the Tanners Kit or a large sewing kit.)<br>
****************************************************<br>
<br>
Othmir Fur cap (Trivial above 250) - Coldain Tanners Kit!<br>
2 Othmir Furs, Silver Thread, Cap Pattern, Vial of Clear Mana <br>
<br>
===========<br>
Required items<br>
===========<br>
<br>
Brewing<br>
---------------------------------------<br>
Heady kiola (Trival at 46)<br>
2 Kiola Sap, Water, Bottle<br>
<br>
Pottery <br>
---------------------------------------<br>
Poison Vial (Trivial at 148)<br>
Small Block of Clay, Vial Sketch, Flask Water <br>
<br>
Some vendors also sell Poison Vials<br>
Example - NPC Toxdil in West Freeport sewers (out the west gate <br>
follow right wall until you pass through the sewer illusionary wall<br>
entrance).<br>
<br>
Enchanter made Vials<br>
----------------------------------------<br>
Vial of Viscous Mana<br>
Spell: Thicken Mana (lvl 12)<br>
Components: Poison Vial, Pearl<br>
Mana cost: 200<br>
Gem cost (best price): 4pp 7gp 2sp 5 cp<br>
<br>
Vial of Clear Mana<br>
Spell: Clarify Mana (lvl 29)<br>
Components: Poison Vial, Emerald<br>
Mana cost: 600<br>
Gem cost (best price): 13pp 6go 5sp  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#330000>- </font><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm>Eq Enchanters Realm</a><font color=#330000> - </font><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmfrm9>Tradeskills</a> <font color=#330000> - </font><a href="http://www.geocities.com/eqenchantersrealm/">Eq Enchanters Realm Main Page</a><font color=#330000> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.245d<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

